## 📌 What Is This File?

`Level1.py` is the **first playable level** of the game. The player must reach the blue door at the far right, but two pranks trigger along the way to trick them.

It imports all shared tools from `main.py` (canvas, clock, fonts, colours, draw functions) and runs its own self-contained game loop.

---

## 🎯 Level Objective

```
Start (left) ──► jump up platforms ──► reach the BLUE DOOR (right side)
```

Simple goal — but two pranks make it harder than it looks.

