## 🧑‍🎮 Player Setup

```python
player    = pygame.Rect(60, 420, 40, 40)  # x, y, width, height
vel_y     = 0        # vertical speed (positive = falling)
gravity   = 0.7      # added to vel_y every frame when airborne
on_ground = False    # only True when standing on something
```

**Physics every frame:**
```python
vel_y    += gravity      # accelerate downward
player.y += int(vel_y)   # move player
```

**Jump:**
```python
if keys[pygame.K_SPACE] and on_ground:
    vel_y = -14    # negative = upward
```

