## 🎮 Game Loop Structure (Every Frame)

```
1. clock.tick(60)          — cap at 60 FPS
2. blink_timer += 1        — advance animation clock
3. Draw background         — sky, stars, buildings, TV, floor
4. Handle events           — QUIT, HOME, RETRY, NEXT LEVEL clicks
5. Player movement         — A/D move, SPACE jump
6. Physics                 — apply gravity, move player.y
7. Collision detection     — floor, plank1, plank2, plank3
8. Prank 1 logic           — slide detection + plank animation
9. Prank 2 logic           — fall + door teleport + slide
10. Win/death detection    — colliderect(door) or player.y <= 0
11. Win animation          — player shrinks over 60 frames
12. Death animation        — pieces explode for 90 frames
13. Level complete         — fireworks spawn every 20 frames
14. Draw platforms/door    — with shadows and glow effects
15. Draw player/pieces/FX  — depending on current game state
16. Draw HUD               — level name + hint text + HOME button
17. Game over screen       — blinking GAME OVER + RETRY button
18. Level clear screen     — rainbow LEVEL CLEAR! + NEXT LEVEL button
19. blit_canvas()          — push everything to the real window
```

