## 🔑 Key Python Concepts Used

| Concept | Where |
|---|---|
| `pygame.Rect` + `colliderect()` | All platform and door collision |
| `nonlocal` keyword | `restore_plank2()` modifies outer scope variables |
| `math.sin()` | Saucer float, lamp pulse, antenna sway, eye look, bubble float |
| `random.seed(77)` | Background stars always appear in the same position |
| `canvas.set_clip()` | Prevents news ticker from drawing outside the TV |
| State machine (string phases) | `door_phase = "up2" / "left2" / "down2"` |
| Particle system | Death pieces + fireworks (list of dicts with physics) |
| `pygame.SRCALPHA` | Semi-transparent overlay for win/game-over darkening |
| List comprehension filter | `fireworks = [fw for fw in fireworks if fw['life'] > 0]` |
| Dynamic import | `from Level2 import level_2` only when NEXT is clicked |

